						               													<description>Let's go skiing with Alberto Tomba!!!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;What's it all about.....&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the game you will play the part of a ski instructor in a large ski resort. The snow is perfect, the slopes are inviting and the facilities for the apres-ski are excellent. In other words the perfect ski surroundings.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Being a ski instructor is a popular profession and your competitors are awaiting their chance. Time and again you must prove your professional skills.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the game you should try to score points off your collegues from the other skiing schools in speed, strategic insight and technique. Of course, you must not act recklessly as you must try to keep your pupils attentive while at the same time producing some results. What will you do? Will you conquer the black slope with the best pupils from your class or do you vote for team building and aim at getting all your pupils on the slope at the same time? Maybe you want to win the game by putting the other teams in a position where they cannot ski any further? Maybe you will decide on your goal during the game and let the situations you meet on your way guide you. It won't be easy to cross the finish first. On the way competing colleagues and unexpected obstacles may cause extra problems. So keep a cool head.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Have fun and good luck!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the box&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
